               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> </gramGrp>, plerumque <gramGrp> <gen value="not found">m.</gen> </gramGrp>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> ver et aestas </quote></cit> [Dubium est, utrum a verbo <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐገየ፡</foreign> (coll. <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܚܓܳܐ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> festum celebravit </quote></cit>) an terminatione adjectivorum <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> âvi </quote></cit> vel <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> âi </quote></cit> a nomine <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐግ፡</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="he">חָג</foreign>) a verbo <foreign xml:lang="he">חגג</foreign> derivatum sit. Illud quoque in medio relinquimus, utrum ejus notio prima <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> tempus festi </quote></cit> vel <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> festorum solemnium </quote></cit> an <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> tempus anni revertentis </quote></cit> (coll. <foreign xml:lang="ar">حِجَّةٌ</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> annus </quote></cit>) fuerit. Sed Geez populum hac voce pariter atque caeteris mensium et anni partium nominibus, prius quam suas in Abyssinia sedes occupavisset, usum ess satis constat]. Primitus <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጸው፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> ver </quote></cit> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸዳይ፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> aestas </quote></cit> communi nomine <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡</foreign> comprehenduntur, nec nisi ubi (per libros in Geez linguam translatos) tria vel quatuor anni tempora distinguuntur, nomen generis in nomen speciei abiit. <sense n="a" xml:id="Da"> Respondet <foreign xml:lang="grc">θέρος</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> aestas </quote></cit> <foreign xml:lang="gez">በሐጋይ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Prov." loc="6,8">Prov. 6,8</ref>; <ref cRef="Prov." loc="26,1">Prov. 26,1</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወሐጋይ፡ ውእቱ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Jud." loc="3,20">Jud. 3,20</ref>; <cb n="0131" xml:id="c0131"/> <ref cRef="2 Reg." loc="23,11">2 Reg. 23,11</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ቤተ፡ ሐጋይ፡</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="grc">ὁ οἶκος ὁ θερινός</foreign> <ref cRef="Am." loc="3,15">Am. 3,15</ref>; <ref cRef="Herm." loc="52 ">Herm. p. 52 </ref>(<lbl expand="oppositum, -o, -nitur">opp.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክረምት፡</foreign>).
</sense> <sense n="b" xml:id="Db"> Ubi duo anni tempora distinguuntur <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡</foreign> semestre aestivum, <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክረምት፡</foreign> hibernum significat: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡ ወክረምት፡</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="grc">θέρος καὶ ἔαρ</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="he">קַיִץ וָחֹרֶף</foreign>) <ref cRef="Gen. " loc="8,22">Gen.  8,22</ref>; <ref cRef="Kuf." loc="6">Kuf. 6</ref>; <ref cRef="Hen." loc="4">Hen. 4</ref>; <ref cRef="Hen." loc="2,3">Hen. 2,3</ref>; Aliis in locis <foreign xml:lang="grc">θέρος καὶ ἔαρ</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="he">קַיִץ וָחֹרֶף</foreign>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክረምት፡ ወሐጋይ፡</foreign> redditur <ref cRef="Zach." loc="14,8">Zach. 14,8</ref>; <ref cRef="Ps." loc="73,18">Ps. 73,18</ref>; <ref cRef="Kuf." loc="29.">Kuf. 29.</ref> Ex his locis tempus <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡</foreign> tempori <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክረምት፡</foreign> oppositum esse apparet.
</sense> <sense n="c" xml:id="Dc"> Inveniuntur loci, ubi <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡</foreign> a <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማእረር፡</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> messe </quote></cit>) distinctum vel <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> tempus vernum et aestatis initium </quote></cit> vel <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> autumnum </quote></cit> significet: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢክረምት፡ ወኢሐጋይ፡ ወኢማእረር፡</foreign> <ref cRef="4 Esr." loc="6,8">4 Esr. 6,8</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወፈለጠ፡ እምውስቴቶሙ፡ ክረምተ፡ ወማእረረ፡ ወሐጋየ፡ በበኍልቆሙ፡ ወበበ፡ ጊዜሆሙ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sir." loc="36,9">Sir. 36,9</ref>.
</sense> <sense n="d" xml:id="Dd"> Quatuor tempora distinguuntur: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክረምት፡ መጸው፡ ማእረር፡ ሐጋይ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Kuf." loc="6">Kuf. p. 6</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸዳይ፡ መፀው፡ ሐጋይ፡ ክረምት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Abush." loc="1">Abush. 1</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸዳይ፡ ሐጋይ፡ መጸው፡ ክረምት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Abush. " loc="39">Abush.  39</ref>; unde <foreign xml:lang="gez">መፀው፡ ሐጋይ፡ ጸዳይ፡</foreign> ab Aethiopibus (ut qui in sua terra quatuor tempora distinguere non consueverint) promiscue usurpari elucet. <ref cRef="At Abush." loc="4,">At Abush. 4,</ref> ubi accuratius de hac re disputatur, ait: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሀለዉ፡ ፬ ዘመናት፤ ቀዳሚሆሙ፡ ዘመነ፡ መጸው፡ ወውእቱ፡ እልሐምል፡ ወልተውር፡ ወልዠውዛ፤ ወዘመነ፡ ሐጋይ፡ እልሰርጣን፡ ውአልሰድ፡ ውሰንብላህ፤ ወዘመነ፡ ጸዳይ፡ እልሚዛን፡ ወአቅረብ፡ ወቀውስ፤ ወዘመነ፡ ክረምት፡ እልዠድይ፡ ወደልው፡ ወልሑት፡</foreign>, unde <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡</foreign> <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> aestatem esse </quote></cit> apparet.
</sense> <sense n="e" xml:id="De"> Denique notandum est, <ref cRef="Job" loc="38,32">Job 38,32</ref> <foreign xml:lang="grc">Μαζουρώθ</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክረምት፡</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="grc">Ἕσπερος</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡</foreign> vertisse Aethiopem. – Videre licet, quae J. Ludolfus in Hist. Aeth. I, 5, 26–33 et Isenbergius in <lbl expand="lexicon">lex.</lbl> amh. p. 93 sub voce <foreign xml:lang="gez">በጋ፡</foreign> de temporibus anni, quae in Aethiopia distinguuntur, eorumque initiis annotaverunt. – <lbl expand="Vocabularium Aethiopicum, -a -a">Voc. Ae.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡ ዘ፡ መዋዕለ፡ በጋ፡</foreign> 
</sense> </sense>
               
            <sense xml:id="Tmain" xml:lang="en" source="#traces"> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote>ḥagāy</quote></cit> <sense n="G"> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡</foreign> <cit type="transcription" xml:lang="gez"><quote>ḥagāy</quote></cit> « deuxième partie de l’année abyssine; commence le 25 du mois de <foreign xml:lang="gez">ታኅሳስ፡</foreign>, 2 janvier, (et va) jusqu’au 24 du mois de <foreign xml:lang="gez">መጋቢት፡</foreign>, (1er avril). Contre Ludolf qui la met après la 3e partie <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸዳይ፡</foreign>» <lb/>
